{"tid":636243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★分析師：iPhone X已死！","createTime":"2018-04-20T16:15:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-20T16:42:49.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cb94ec49b81153b0d6fedee99bd74e437e2bcbb7","tid":636243,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T16:15:18.000Z","msg":"證券商Mirabaud Securities麾下專注科技行業的全球主題小組聯席主管坎普林(Neil Campling)認為，最令他擔心的問題之一在於晶片供應過剩，因為蘋果公司的iPhone X已死。<br />\n<br />\n坎普林表示，iPhone X只有一個致命的缺點，那就是售價太高昂，消費者唾棄價格過高的智能電話。不過，他認為蘋果的原有庫存iPhone X機型還會繼續上市銷售，但公司不會再生產了。<br />\n<br />\n在台積電公布財報後，許多分析師都警告稱，蘋果公司第一季度的iPhone銷售可能會低於預期。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180420/bkn-20180420230403628-0420_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180420%2Fbkn-20180420230403628-0420_00842_001.html&d=OhHl2%2FNXh7Khe42hTWzVOpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=a44cddb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180420/bkn-20180420230403628-0420_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"315d574b229d67853b916ca76a74bdc444558d26","tid":636243,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T16:15:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa3dcfd4a1b77b0019e56a98a3df9fb154638aed","tid":636243,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"315d574b229d67853b916ca76a74bdc444558d26","tid":636243,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T16:15:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/no